The Board of Bitherium is made up of many people from different walks of life all around the world. Our vision is to improve and
develop the Cryptocurrency concept while maintaining its original objectives. Namely: Unanimity as well as decentralization.
Our work focusses on making crypto accessible to the masses. In order to achieve the necessary acceptance and adoption, our
prerequisites must be fundamentally solid, transparent and user-friendly.
One of the major fundamentals in this sphere is the merger of the financial sector and the crypto currency speculation market.
This requires managing/mitigating financial risk and keeping it as low as possible while pushing returns and profits to be as high
This is the reason behind the decision of having investment risk in Bitherium at a low-level right from the start. In addition to
maintaining investment risk, the Exchange is set up in a way that is lucrative and profitable to investors. We have opted to provide
and connect our own token to daily transactions and trades taking place on the exchange in terms of profit sharing which makes
our token an ideal long-term as well as short-term investment.
As a short-term investment, Bitherium gives investors the opportunity to speculate on lucrative profits. This is because the
exchange trading volume influences the value of each token.
For long term investment, our token holds the important property and concept of Profit Sharing. This means that 50% of the net
profit of the exchange will be paid out and distributed (at least once a year) to all token holders. Thus, maintaining a healthy
Growth rate in Bitherium price and value.
